SomniaAgentConsumer::handleResponse
├── when the caller is not the platform
│   └── it should revert.
└── when the caller is the platform
    ├── given the request id is not pending
    │   └── it should revert.
    └── given the request id is pending
        ├── it should clear the pending flag before dispatching.
        ├── it should dispatch to _onResult with the responses and the status.
        ├── given the status is Success with at least one response
        │   └── it should dispatch with the successful responses.
        ├── given the status is Failed or TimedOut
        │   └── it should dispatch with the failure status and not revert.
        └── given the same request id is delivered a second time
            └── it should revert.
